This command allows you to pick up items without anyone
else knowing you picked them up. It works exactly like
"get" or "take". You can use "palm all". A thief must
always be the master of deception, so quickly palm that
item and don't let others see you've picked it up. You
must be guild level 4 to use this power.

Syntax: palm <item> or "all", or palm <item> from <target>,
        as well as 'palm all from <target>'.

